Project Intent
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

AutoResearch Chain is intended to be a trustless market for useful AI research
work. The project’s design philosophy is that adversarial incentives should be
structured so that participants are economically motivated to propose, validate,
challenge, and refine improvements to AI training recipes.

The value of the system is the research output.
Blockchain is the mechanism that enables a permissionless, auditable,
non-custodial market for that research.

